'''Hotelka raffles'''

Raffles Hotels & Resorts waa silsilado hudheelo raaxo leh oo ay leedahay shirkadda AccorHotels tan iyo sannadka 2016-ka. Waxa la asaasay 1887 iyadoo la furayo asal ahaan Raffles Hotel ee Singapore, shirkaddu waxay bilowday inay horumariso caalamka dhammaadkii 1990-meeyadii. Waxay heshay Swissôtel 2001-dii. Laga bilaabo November 2017, Raffles Hotels & Resorts waxay ku shaqaysaa 11 hudheel oo raaxo ah.

